mars.name: Mission to Mars 2049
mars.title: Board Game
mars.description: Mission to Mars 2049 is a board game I invented and designed in 2013-2014. It successfully raised funds needed to get publish via crowdfunding and several seed investment pitches in 2015. In 2016-2017 it participated in several of the largest toy and board game conventions in the world, got published in seven languages, sold over 16'000 copies world-wide and briefly reached Top 10 best-selling board games in Germany and Top 20 in the UK.
